descriptionHtml:
Beautiful (for my taste) miniature Breton girl. Clean savegame. Near the 3 guardian stones  between Helgen and Riverwood. No cheats. Vanilla equipment.
I use:
- Coverwomen http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563 (look #3)
- Pretty Eyes by pikkatze http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=3424
- CBBE v2 http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2666
It is desirable for best results. 
I hope you enjoy this character!
author: ortog
